          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "What is Semantic Kernel?"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Semantic Kernel (SK) is Microsoft's open-source AI orchestration SDK for Python, C#, and Java. It lets you compose AI capabilities \u2014 LLM calls, code functions, and memory \u2014 into \"plugins\" that a central "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Kernel",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "code"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " object can invoke and chain. Unlike LangChain's chain metaphor or LlamaIndex's document focus, SK is structured around the plugin-as-skill model familiar from Microsoft 365 Copilot's architecture."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Kernel:",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": " the hub that holds LLM services, memory, plugins, and configuration"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Plugin:",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": " a named group of related "
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "KernelFunction",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "code"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": " objects (Python functions decorated with "
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "@kernel_function",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "code"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": ")"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
